'''Public Debate = website to observe public debate over the internet, and to develop tools to enhance them.'''


URL = http://www.publicdebate.net



=Description=

"a place where registered members can, through the observatories, publish their own critical assessments on debates, comment on the associated techniques and discuss the existing assessments.
Members can also publish information about events related to public debates."
(http://www.debatpublic.net/)

An initiative of Philippe Aigrain, author of [[Cause Commune]]


